#, fuzzy
msgid "We released Quarkus 3.32.3, a regular maintenance release."
msgstr "我们发布了 Quarkus 3.32.3，这是一个定期维护版本。"

#: _posts/2026-03-11-quarkus-3-32-3-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Today, we released Quarkus 3.32.3, the second maintenance release for our 3."
"32 stream (we skipped 3.32.0)."
